# Peer Repository Registry\n\nThis module provides a registry for peer repositories in the hub federation.\n\n## Usage\n\n```python\nfrom hub.federation.registry import PeerRegistry\n\n# Create a new peer registry\nregistry = PeerRegistry()\n\n# Add a new peer repository\nregistry.add_peer('https://example.com/repo.git', 'node_id', 'public_key_fingerprint')\n\n# Get all peer repositories\npeers = registry.get_peers()\n```
